1
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:40,796
This is the Foochow Road in Shanghai

2
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:44,919
In 1922 Ma Yung Chen was ambushed
at Qing Lin tower

3
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:48,874
and was mortally injured

4
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:53,192
He was surrounded by many people
who axed him to death

5
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:56,471
It's been more than 20 years

6
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,830
and the Foochow Road has changed

7
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,672
but only on the outside;

8
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,478
Inside it is filled with low-lives

9
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,113
Ma Yung Chen of Shangtung

10
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:06,840
has become a legend

11
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:08,678
A similar tragedy is about to

12
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:11,712
re-enact in this place

13
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,990
The hero's name has changed naturally

14
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:16,628
Our protagonist is a famous person
in this vicinity

15
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,518
Qiu Lian Huan

16
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:32,198
Master Qiu

17
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:47,158
Mr. Yu, is this wine alright?

18
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,790
Mr. Yu, this wine…

19
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,953
Get lost

20
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,478
What? Haven't decided yet?

21
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,874
King

22
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,751
Would it be a straight?

23
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,319
Xiao Kai likes card games

24
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,879
It might be a straight

25
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,272
Your turn to call

26
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,469
Marvellous

27
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,233
One dollar

28
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,873
How much do you still have?

29
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,838
Not less than you

30
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,557
You want to chicken out?

31
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:59,192
Here's 23 grand, you may give up
if you have no guts

32
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,594
A full house

33
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:31,194
Damn, I've lost again

34
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,193
Ju Fang, let's go

35
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:53,833
Xiao Kai, don't go,
you haven't lost much today

36
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,632
I suggest you go too

37
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,716
the cards are possessed by a ghost today

38
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,791
Hey, mind what you say

39
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,319
What I say is clear enough

40
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:09,638
Kid, if you can't bear to lose, don't play

41
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:21,999
It's for you to buy candy
for your girlfriend

42
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:38,475
Jin Xi Fu, bring him over

43
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,680
We're all here just for fun, stop

44
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:01,437
I'll come over myself

45
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:29,789
Let him go, he's not such a tough guy

46
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,238
Ju Fang

47
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,673
Who is this woman?

48
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:07,389
The famous socialite
Shen Ju Fang of Shanghai

49
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:09,238
You don't know her?

50
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,429
I must say

51
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,158
why did you fight with Xiao Kai?

52
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,673
His father is not a nice guy

53
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:14,431
Right

54
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,352
I know

55
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:40,794
Qiu Lian Huan? Who is he?

56
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:45,399
How come you sit at
the same table with his kind?

57
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:58,797
Boss, you've been away
from the scene for a while

58
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:02,077
and don't know about the new upstarts

59
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:04,111
This Qiu Lian Huan is quite well known

60
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:06,117
around Foochow road

61
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,719
Enough to cause me problems?

62
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,989
Of course not

63
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:14,789
Who in Shanghai dares do that?

64
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,078
Get my card and bring that

65
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,593
Qiu Lian Huan to see me

66
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,670
Yes

67
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,473
Go…

68
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:32,954
If you need money
get it from the treasurer

69
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:40,193
Boss, Xiao Kai has grown up

70
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,999
you should hand over your affairs to him

71
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,874
Gen Bao, we're old friends

72
00:09:47,040 --> 00:09:50,396
don't pull my leg

73
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,715
He isn't of such calibre

74
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:56,839
Our affairs still require our own efforts

75
00:09:57,000 --> 00:10:01,710
The city still unsettled
as the Japanese have just left

76
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:04,479
we can use the opportunity

77
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:07,034
to make a quick buck

78
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:23,435
Over there, the ball is over there

79
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,115
Well?

80
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:35,716
Forget it,
that woman is kept by Yu Xiao Kai

81
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,233
I haven't even stepped into the front door

82
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:39,874
Nonsense, you didn't say I want to see her

83
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,752
I did

84
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,559
The doorman said he's never heard of you

85
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:51,037
It's over there. Ask him

86
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,959
Give us back the ball…

87
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:59,588
You fought with them?

88
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:08,556
Right, my name is not as

89
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:13,111
popular as tycoons like
Yu Zhen Ting Zeng Gen Bao

90
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,157
It's still a long way off

91
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,559
He kicked it far away

92
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:30,232
That's why
we want to kick these people away

93
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,549
So we would not be over-shadowed by them

94
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,948
You…

95
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:36,472
Well? Are you afraid?

96
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:37,755
It's not that

97
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:40,912
it's just that no one has ever
messed with them

98
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:44,308
Someone has to sooner or later

99
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,913
You go back first

100
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:47,029
If anyone asks say I am at

101
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,714
the home of Shen Ju Fang at Yu Yuan Road

102
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:51,876
That woman has over 10 people
guarding her door

103
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:52,677
If you went there…

104
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:56,196
That's precisely why I want to go there

105
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,640
You will run into trouble I'm afraid

106
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,788
"Shen Residence"

107
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,116
Hey, what are you doing?

108
00:12:42,520 --> 00:12:44,590
I want to see Miss Shen

109
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,478
Who are you?

110
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:50,111
I am Qiu Lian Huan

111
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,389
Damn you

112
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,914
You want me to charge in?

113
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:20,310
Do you know what this place is?

114
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,276
Shen residence

115
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,628
Mr. Yu is here

116
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,034
Save it

117
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:28,318
What ajoke, it doesn't say
'Yu Residence' on the door

118
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,908
I am here to see the master of the house

119
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,953
Alright, if you go in

120
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,793
I'm sure you'll come out deadl

121
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:13,153
Miss Shen, it's so difficult to see you

122
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,433
Get out

123
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,716
Ask them to get out

124
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:26,632
You get out

125
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,513
You're mistaken

126
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:30,079
Not at all

127
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:33,158
An upstart like you is lucky

128
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:35,390
to see me twice

129
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,274
Alright

130
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,836
"Yu Zhen Ting"

131
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:11,075
Master Yu likes to invite
Master Qiu over for dinner

132
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,477
As Master Qiu is not here we cannot decide

133
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:18,355
No one dares to decline
an invitation from Master Yu

134
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:23,592
I am bringing you the message,
it's just the same

135
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:25,239
That's not true

136
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:28,790
Master Qiu is with Miss Shen

137
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,757
you must know that place well

138
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:33,229
please make the trip again

139
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:37,158
If Yu Xiao Kai is there as well

140
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:41,438
it'd be easy to clear things up

141
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,429
Please go back

142
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,389
Let's go

143
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:04,274
If we get on Yu Zhen Ting's nerve
we'll be in trouble

144
00:17:07,520 --> 00:17:10,353
I know, but we have no choice

145
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:17,634
You nincompoops

146
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:31,192
What difference does it make
even if you were there?

147
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,591
Alright, Qiu Lian Huan

148
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:50,672
I will teach you a lesson for this

149
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:54,712
What's the use of your anger here?

150
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,552
Go and speak to him

151
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:05,999
Prepare the car, I'm off to see my dad

152
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,189
Yes

153
00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:32,273
I think this kid Qiu Lian Huan

154
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:35,000
will not give you face

155
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:39,793
I don't think so, who does he think he is?

156
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:51,992
Real good

157
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:54,196
This isn't like our old time

158
00:18:55,040 --> 00:18:56,109
What's the matter?

159
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,110
Master Zeng

160
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:59,435
This afternoon
Qiu Lian Huan went to the girl who

161
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:02,034
was kept by Xiao Kai and caused trouble

162
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,792
He injured many people there

163
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,279
We let him escape again

164
00:19:07,040 --> 00:19:08,712
Old man

165
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:13,792
We can't stay in Shanghai anymore

166
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:14,989
let's move to Mongolia

167
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,673
What are you shouting?

168
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:20,678
Ask our men to seek out Qiu Lian Huan

169
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:23,070
regardless of where he is
and what he's doing

170
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,076
bring him to me

171
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,309
Yes

172
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:31,551
I'll go back and ask our men to find him

173
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:34,518
We can't let him go on like this

174
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:38,716
But let's not make a big deal

175
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:41,314
or we'll exaggerate his importance

176
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:43,230
I'll go too

177
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:45,914
When I find him I'll teach him a lesson

178
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,149
Jin Xi Fu, come with me

179
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:48,269
Yes

180
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,672
I'll go too and make arrangements

181
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:53,273
Don't be nervous

182
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,998
remember who we are

183
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:57,873
we are used to his kind

184
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,274
They want to charge in

185
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:02,273
but will end up all dead

186
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:04,868
Master, I've heard things
about this Qiu Lian Huan

187
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:07,150
people say he is not afraid of death

188
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:09,754
but he can't do anything to us

189
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:14,869
But Xiao Kai is attracting
too much attention outside

190
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:15,950
You mean…

191
00:20:16,120 --> 00:20:17,553
I was just guessing

192
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,790
Ask Xiao Kai to be more careful

193
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:23,392
I'm leaving

194
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,232
Master Zeng

195
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,233
Come here, everyone

196
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:47,875
Business is here

197
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:49,792
Go to Bai Sin Bridge again

198
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:50,750
ask a few men to come here

199
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:51,915
Yes

200
00:20:53,360 --> 00:20:54,429
Let's go

201
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:57,634
Put in your efforts, everyone

202
00:20:57,760 --> 00:21:00,672
We'll teach Qiu Lian Huan
a good lesson tonight

203
00:22:10,760 --> 00:22:12,273
Master Qiu

204
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:54,870
Thanks

205
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,354
Thanks…

206
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:19,476
You…

207
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:25,078
Trying to put on airs? I must get you

208
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:27,714
You've already got me

209
00:23:28,120 --> 00:23:29,633
I didn't mean you

210
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:11,108
Don't think we wouldn't hit back

211
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:15,432
That's exactly what I want you to do

212
00:24:16,040 --> 00:24:19,157
Jin Xi Fu, bring him over

213
00:25:03,520 --> 00:25:05,829
Where is Qiu Lian Huan? Speak

214
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,079
Beat him

215
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:12,309
Damn you

216
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:27,476
It doesn't matter if you don't speak

217
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:29,989
we'll wait here till he returns

218
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:31,635
Let him go

219
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:15,999
Qiu Lian Huan is back

220
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,357
Master Qiu

221
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:30,119
Many people came to your home
but haven't left

222
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:09,794
No, don't

223
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:34,280
Brother Qiu, you're back

224
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,678
Geng Sheng, don't worry

225
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:37,989
Whatever they did to you

226
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:39,872
we'll do the same to them

227
00:28:56,800 --> 00:29:00,429
You messed up my place

228
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:02,397
You should say something

229
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:07,191
I'll pay…

230
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:09,237
What about my men who have been injured?

231
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:14,235
I'll get them the best doctor

232
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:16,950
Master Qiu,
you have been given enough face

233
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:18,838
let Xiao Kai go

234
00:29:20,280 --> 00:29:22,714
Nonsense, you charged in this place

235
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:25,155
and still say I've been given face?

236
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:28,319
Just tell us what you want

237
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:31,276
What's the use of talking to you

238
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:34,238
I'll take you to your dad

239
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:39,038
Alright, let me go first

240
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:40,758
We'll go this way

241
00:29:42,120 --> 00:29:47,592
Boss…he came too fast

242
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:50,320
and got right to Xiao Kai

243
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,310
l…

244
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:52,708
Enough

245
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:14,758
Get the sitting room ready
to welcome the guest

246
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:15,949
Yes

247
00:30:16,240 --> 00:30:17,229
Go out all of you

248
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,992
Yes

249
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,110
He's here

250
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:43,797
How many men has he brought?

251
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:46,793
None, just him and Xiao Kai

252
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:15,756
Master Qiu, thanks for bringing him

253
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:18,675
I admire your courage to come alone

254
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:21,115
Someone like you has appeared in Shanghai

255
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:22,798
it's ajoke

256
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:25,394
we could have missed you

257
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:28,034
Xiao Kai is still young

258
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:31,192
and is backed by Master Yu

259
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:34,837
if I used too much force, please pardon me

260
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:39,232
No, someone should teach him a lesson

261
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:51,598
Don't…

262
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:03,396
What are you standing there for?

263
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:19,153
Get in

264
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:30,910
Wait, the woman you harbour

265
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:33,315
is not a proper person

266
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:35,232
If Master Qiu likes her

267
00:32:35,360 --> 00:32:37,396
then you stop seeing her

268
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:38,999
No way

269
00:32:40,800 --> 00:32:43,951
Have you not had enough? Get inside

270
00:32:56,760 --> 00:32:58,079
Please sit

271
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:04,436
I am old now

272
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:08,832
but I too feared nothing when I was young

273
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:10,719
Please sit

274
00:33:17,840 --> 00:33:20,229
Let this matter rest

275
00:33:20,360 --> 00:33:22,715
Thanks for bringing him back

276
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:25,553
I'll pay for the damages

277
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:28,075
It's okay, I can afford them

278
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:32,352
Master Sua,
Xiao Kai needs to retain his credibility

279
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:36,559
he won't mention this incident,
how about you?

280
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:40,759
Don't worry

281
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:45,230
if we hadn't fought, we wouldn't have met

282
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:49,075
Master Qiu, please take care

283
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:54,273
You are too kind

284
00:33:57,760 --> 00:34:01,309
My men are anxious for my return

285
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,475
I must go

286
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:03,999
Please

287
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,956
Call Master Zeng

288
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:29,954
Hello, yes

289
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,998
Call from the Yu Residence

290
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,799
Hello

291
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:43,753
Really?

292
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:47,917
Alright, I'll come…

293
00:35:03,920 --> 00:35:05,831
I think Yu Zhen Ting wants me

294
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,070
to deal with Qiu Lian Huan

295
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:09,349
Then we…

296
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:11,954
He is too old

297
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:15,078
and should retire

298
00:35:24,640 --> 00:35:28,076
but he insists on staying

299
00:35:28,240 --> 00:35:31,755
I have a plan, Xiao Kai is his life

300
00:35:58,520 --> 00:35:59,999
Tell Miss Shen, Master Qiu is here

301
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:01,434
Yes

302
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:29,713
I'm here

303
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:31,359
Please sit

304
00:36:31,520 --> 00:36:34,034
Master Yu called me

305
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:36,473
I'm all yours

306
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:41,352
You don't seem happy to see me

307
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:43,317
What has that to do with anything?

308
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:46,119
You like me and have got me

309
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,633
isn't that enough?

310
00:36:49,080 --> 00:36:51,150
You like Xiao Kai

311
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:57,359
Xiao Kai? I merely pity him

312
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:03,435
I can give you whatever he could give you

313
00:37:04,120 --> 00:37:07,999
Right, any man can give me that

314
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:11,918
Don't take me for any man

315
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:14,436
What's the difference?

316
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:25,235
You'll know in time

317
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:37,397
Let's go

318
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:39,112
Boss, where to?

319
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,554
Go back

320
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,679
Hey, do you know how to drive?

321
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:08,638
Sorry, I lost control

322
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:09,869
Sorry is not enough

323
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:18,679
Forget it. Let's see if the car can start

324
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:20,518
don't bother with this kind of people

325
00:38:20,680 --> 00:38:21,510
Yes

326
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:41,068
Attack

327
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:18,390
Master Qiu, please come with us

328
00:41:18,560 --> 00:41:20,630
and you'll not suffer

329
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,995
Who's your boss?

330
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:28,469
It's Master Yu naturally

331
00:41:28,640 --> 00:41:32,349
He wouldn't do such a lowly thing

332
00:43:24,160 --> 00:43:25,275
You…

333
00:43:26,680 --> 00:43:27,874
Sit aside

334
00:43:58,440 --> 00:43:59,953
Why have you got into so much trouble?

335
00:44:00,120 --> 00:44:01,348
To have to fight against Yu Zhen Ting
is bad enough

336
00:44:01,520 --> 00:44:03,317
and now you provoke Zeng Gen Bao too

337
00:44:06,720 --> 00:44:09,518
They are his men?

338
00:44:12,240 --> 00:44:19,430
We either destroy others or be destroyed

339
00:44:32,800 --> 00:44:34,438
Blood?

340
00:44:36,280 --> 00:44:38,236
It's mine

341
00:44:53,560 --> 00:44:54,470
Let's go

342
00:45:14,880 --> 00:45:18,589
If we don't deal with him

343
00:45:20,680 --> 00:45:22,591
I don't know what he'll do

344
00:45:22,760 --> 00:45:24,512
He's ruthless enough

345
00:45:31,920 --> 00:45:32,352
Don't worry, I'll take care of it

346
00:45:32,520 --> 00:45:34,795
and avenge Xiao Kai

347
00:45:34,960 --> 00:45:36,518
Thank you, uncle

348
00:45:40,360 --> 00:45:42,920
Qiu Lian Huan is no nice guy

349
00:45:44,200 --> 00:45:47,590
Boss, it's best Xiao Kai went out less

350
00:45:51,160 --> 00:45:53,879
I'm not afraid of him,
I'll deliberately go outside

351
00:45:55,840 --> 00:45:58,070
Then take more men with you

352
00:46:04,120 --> 00:46:06,873
I'm going, contact me if you need anything

353
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:08,035
Alright

354
00:46:21,240 --> 00:46:23,754
Am I getting old?

355
00:46:25,280 --> 00:46:29,239
I can't even deal with such a person

356
00:47:39,400 --> 00:47:42,551
Miss Shen, I'm going

357
00:47:46,320 --> 00:47:48,231
Don't play tough

358
00:47:48,400 --> 00:47:49,719
you're seriously wounded

359
00:47:49,880 --> 00:47:51,996
If you bump into Zeng Gen Bao's men

360
00:47:52,160 --> 00:47:53,559
you'll be dead

361
00:47:54,000 --> 00:47:57,117
You know he established himself
by the Knife gang

362
00:47:57,280 --> 00:47:59,350
they are desperados

363
00:47:59,520 --> 00:48:01,988
I don't want your pity

364
00:48:02,160 --> 00:48:04,594
like you pity Xiao Kai

365
00:48:05,960 --> 00:48:07,393
Don't go

366
00:48:14,520 --> 00:48:17,637
No one will know you are resting here

367
00:48:21,560 --> 00:48:27,635
I am not pitying you, I want to help you

368
00:48:41,800 --> 00:48:45,793
Is it worth it suffering for a woman?

369
00:48:45,960 --> 00:48:47,871
It's not only for you

370
00:48:48,040 --> 00:48:50,474
I've gone too far on this course

371
00:48:50,640 --> 00:48:53,029
and will end up like this one day

372
00:49:19,320 --> 00:49:21,436
I told you so

373
00:49:21,600 --> 00:49:23,352
Qiu Lian Huan is no nice guy

374
00:49:23,520 --> 00:49:25,636
Why don't you find out
how many men he's brought?

375
00:49:25,800 --> 00:49:26,755
He has only three men

376
00:49:26,920 --> 00:49:27,989
We have over ten people

377
00:49:28,160 --> 00:49:29,832
we could get him back

378
00:49:29,960 --> 00:49:32,315
Get him back? Where is he?

379
00:49:39,320 --> 00:49:40,992
He must be wounded

380
00:49:41,160 --> 00:49:42,513
Even if he's gone into hiding

381
00:49:42,640 --> 00:49:43,914
we could get his whereabouts from his men

382
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:46,395
with a bit of force

383
00:49:46,560 --> 00:49:47,197
Then do it now

384
00:49:47,360 --> 00:49:49,828
Yes…let's go

385
00:49:50,840 --> 00:49:52,910
We'll deal with Yu Xiao Kai's matter later

386
00:49:53,080 --> 00:49:54,229
Yes…

387
00:50:06,840 --> 00:50:07,955
Let's go

388
00:50:14,080 --> 00:50:15,069
Go

389
00:50:15,920 --> 00:50:17,273
Don't move

390
00:50:24,000 --> 00:50:25,319
Is Master Qiu here?

391
00:50:25,480 --> 00:50:27,994
No, you're…

392
00:50:38,120 --> 00:50:39,269
What's the matter?

393
00:50:48,720 --> 00:50:51,359
Lin Geng Sheng, someone's looking for you

394
00:50:53,120 --> 00:50:54,235
Who?

395
00:50:56,600 --> 00:50:58,591
Master Zeng Gen Bao

396
00:50:59,480 --> 00:51:01,516
Who am I

397
00:51:01,680 --> 00:51:02,908
to have such an honourl

398
00:51:03,080 --> 00:51:04,672
What does he want me for?

399
00:51:05,120 --> 00:51:06,678
Are you going or not?

400
00:51:06,840 --> 00:51:08,751
What's to fear?

401
00:51:10,360 --> 00:51:13,193
My life is cheap

402
00:51:13,360 --> 00:51:15,351
it matters not even if I die

403
00:51:17,520 --> 00:51:18,839
So resolute

404
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:23,152
Don't worry,
Master Zeng will treat you well

405
00:51:30,000 --> 00:51:31,274
Let's go and look inside

406
00:51:31,440 --> 00:51:33,556
If Master Qiu is in
please invite him to come along

407
00:51:33,720 --> 00:51:34,755
Yes

408
00:51:44,560 --> 00:51:46,312
Master Qiu is not here

409
00:51:47,320 --> 00:51:48,070
What has happened to him?

410
00:51:48,200 --> 00:51:49,110
Not that serious

411
00:51:49,240 --> 00:51:51,674
He killed Master Zeng's men

412
00:51:51,840 --> 00:51:53,592
He has not returned since going out

413
00:51:53,760 --> 00:51:55,671
I don't know where he has gone

414
00:51:56,520 --> 00:51:57,669
Tell Master Zeng by yourself

415
00:51:58,360 --> 00:52:00,271
I don't know where he has gone

416
00:52:00,440 --> 00:52:03,671
If he's injured where would he seek help?

417
00:52:03,840 --> 00:52:05,398
I don't know

418
00:52:05,920 --> 00:52:09,071
Qiu Lian Huan is tough

419
00:52:09,240 --> 00:52:11,117
I little expect his man to be tough too

420
00:52:12,440 --> 00:52:14,396
I tell you I want to find him

421
00:52:14,560 --> 00:52:16,073
regardless of where he's hiding

422
00:52:16,240 --> 00:52:17,593
I'll find him

423
00:52:17,760 --> 00:52:19,557
Then look for him yourself

424
00:52:19,720 --> 00:52:21,915
When I find him

425
00:52:22,040 --> 00:52:25,794
you will have trouble

426
00:52:27,680 --> 00:52:30,752
Apart from you, Master Qiu

427
00:52:30,920 --> 00:52:34,913
has 54 men, right?

428
00:52:35,080 --> 00:52:36,832
How do you know that?

429
00:52:39,120 --> 00:52:41,759
I've bought 48 of them

430
00:52:41,920 --> 00:52:44,229
but 6 refused

431
00:52:45,200 --> 00:52:46,315
They have all been eliminated

432
00:52:46,480 --> 00:52:47,993
You are cruel

433
00:52:51,320 --> 00:52:55,199
Lin Geng Sheng,
you're of course worth more

434
00:52:56,680 --> 00:52:59,956
How about ten?

435
00:53:04,160 --> 00:53:05,673
Well?

436
00:53:08,040 --> 00:53:11,271
My relation with Master Qiu
is not for sale

437
00:53:11,720 --> 00:53:14,951
Alright, go then

438
00:53:15,120 --> 00:53:17,475
See him out properly

439
00:53:50,600 --> 00:53:53,273
It's okay, please return

440
00:53:53,440 --> 00:53:55,158
We want to see that you die

441
00:55:04,600 --> 00:55:06,955
Tell Zeng Gen Bao

442
00:55:12,720 --> 00:55:15,632
even if I die today

443
00:55:23,200 --> 00:55:26,988
Stuff these into his stomach
and put him in a bag

444
00:55:57,040 --> 00:55:58,029
Let's go

445
00:57:16,720 --> 00:57:20,395
I must call Lin Geng Sheng
so he'll not worry

446
00:57:23,360 --> 00:57:25,032
Do it tomorrow

447
00:57:45,000 --> 00:57:47,116
Hello, yes, Master Qiu

448
00:57:47,280 --> 00:57:48,156
Nothing much, looking for Lin Geng Sheng

449
00:57:48,320 --> 00:57:49,309
Looking for Lin Geng Sheng?

450
00:57:49,480 --> 00:57:51,357
Master Qiu, where are you?

451
00:57:51,520 --> 00:57:52,555
Who are you?

452
00:57:52,720 --> 00:57:56,713
Master Qiu, I am Ah Mo

453
00:57:56,840 --> 00:57:59,035
just tell me what you want

454
00:57:59,200 --> 00:58:00,758
Where are you?

455
00:58:00,920 --> 00:58:04,549
Right, get Lin Geng Sheng on the phone

456
00:58:05,920 --> 00:58:06,875
He has gone out

457
00:58:07,040 --> 00:58:09,600
What's your number? When he comes back…

458
00:58:23,160 --> 00:58:26,232
No, I must go back

459
00:58:26,360 --> 00:58:27,713
something must be wrong

460
00:58:27,880 --> 00:58:30,474
In that case
you should all the more not go out

461
00:58:30,600 --> 00:58:32,272
I'll investigate for you

462
00:58:34,640 --> 00:58:38,519
Alright, but you can't say I am here

463
00:58:39,040 --> 00:58:40,758
I am no fool

464
00:58:50,920 --> 00:58:53,229
I've bought Qiu Lian Huan's all men

465
00:58:53,360 --> 00:58:56,716
I've also filled
Lin Geng Sheng's stomach with lead

466
00:58:56,840 --> 00:58:58,398
and threw him into the Wang Pao river

467
00:58:58,560 --> 00:59:00,471
Qiu Lian Huan must have
fled to the village for fear

468
00:59:00,640 --> 00:59:02,915
and dare not come to Shanghai

469
00:59:03,080 --> 00:59:07,153
Doesn't seem like
how Qiu Lian Huan would handle things

470
00:59:09,440 --> 00:59:16,596
Xiao Kai, Shen Ju Fang is yours again

471
00:59:19,960 --> 00:59:23,236
The boss is getting old,
he's much too concerned

472
00:59:23,680 --> 00:59:25,238
Uncle, you're right

473
00:59:36,520 --> 00:59:38,112
I've won again today

474
00:59:58,400 --> 00:59:59,992
Smells good

475
01:00:02,160 --> 01:00:04,071
So sweet

476
01:00:06,560 --> 01:00:07,834
Naughty

477
01:00:18,000 --> 01:00:19,115
It looks like we miss one person today

478
01:00:19,280 --> 01:00:21,555
Qiu Lian Huan is finished

479
01:00:21,680 --> 01:00:22,795
Don't mention him again

480
01:00:22,960 --> 01:00:26,873
His men have been bought by Master Zeng

481
01:00:28,320 --> 01:00:32,108
What about his assistant Lin Geng Sheng?

482
01:00:36,640 --> 01:00:38,073
His stomach has been filled with lead

483
01:00:38,200 --> 01:00:41,351
and he has been drowned

484
01:00:48,240 --> 01:00:49,468
Hello

485
01:00:50,600 --> 01:00:52,158
Xiao Kai is really good

486
01:00:52,800 --> 01:00:54,358
Sir, your telephone

487
01:00:57,000 --> 01:01:00,993
Hello, alright

488
01:01:01,120 --> 01:01:03,076
Wait till I've arrived,
don't beat him up yet

489
01:01:03,240 --> 01:01:05,879
When I get there
I'll give him a painful time

490
01:01:08,960 --> 01:01:10,518
We've found Qiu Lian Huan

491
01:01:10,680 --> 01:01:12,875
Let me give him a hard time first

492
01:01:13,600 --> 01:01:16,068
Where did you find him?

493
01:01:16,720 --> 01:01:18,711
In the village of Pui Tung

494
01:01:24,240 --> 01:01:26,515
Wait for me at home tonight

495
01:02:13,080 --> 01:02:15,719
Coming, hurry

496
01:02:21,000 --> 01:02:22,433
Stop running, stand still

497
01:02:27,600 --> 01:02:29,477
If you want to fight, go elsewhere

498
01:03:00,760 --> 01:03:02,193
We're Master Qiu's brothers, hear that?

499
01:03:02,360 --> 01:03:03,554
Yes

500
01:04:17,320 --> 01:04:18,753
Quickly…

501
01:04:45,240 --> 01:04:47,470
You're still here

502
01:04:48,760 --> 01:04:49,909
What's the matter?

503
01:04:50,840 --> 01:04:54,389
Xiao Kai received a call
saying that you've been caught

504
01:04:55,800 --> 01:04:56,994
It must be ajoke

505
01:05:01,200 --> 01:05:02,997
I don't think so

506
01:05:03,160 --> 01:05:05,310
It was a call from a friend

507
01:05:05,480 --> 01:05:07,311
He left right away after he hung up

508
01:05:07,480 --> 01:05:09,232
Never mind him

509
01:05:09,400 --> 01:05:11,914
What news have you got?

510
01:05:17,840 --> 01:05:19,478
What about it?

511
01:05:20,280 --> 01:05:21,679
You're finished

512
01:05:24,840 --> 01:05:26,034
How can I?

513
01:05:26,200 --> 01:05:29,397
Zeng Gen Bao has bought off all your men

514
01:05:29,520 --> 01:05:31,556
Each one has been well paid

515
01:05:33,840 --> 01:05:37,469
What about Lin Geng Sheng?
He won't betray me

516
01:05:37,640 --> 01:05:41,315
They threw Lin Geng Sheng

517
01:05:41,480 --> 01:05:43,596
down into the river

518
01:05:51,000 --> 01:05:54,197
You're all by yourself now,
you haven't recuperated yet

519
01:05:54,320 --> 01:05:55,594
You'll kill yourself

520
01:05:55,720 --> 01:05:59,076
Yes, I'd better go on hiding

521
01:05:59,240 --> 01:06:03,392
Hide at a woman's home and be a coward

522
01:06:03,520 --> 01:06:05,272
and dare not see people

523
01:06:06,640 --> 01:06:10,076
Qiu Lian Huan, watch your mouth

524
01:06:10,240 --> 01:06:13,277
I'm at your mercy, and this is your place

525
01:06:19,320 --> 01:06:23,154
You can do whatever you want
after you've recuperated

526
01:06:24,120 --> 01:06:26,395
Now, sit down

527
01:06:26,560 --> 01:06:27,834
I've no time

528
01:06:30,240 --> 01:06:32,470
I still have a lot of friends

529
01:06:32,640 --> 01:06:34,073
I'll go and find them

530
01:06:34,600 --> 01:06:36,272
I have a lot of friends

531
01:06:38,040 --> 01:06:39,996
Don't trust those scumbags

532
01:06:40,120 --> 01:06:44,079
They are my friends, they are like me

533
01:06:45,120 --> 01:06:46,872
They are like Zeng Gen Bao too

534
01:06:47,400 --> 01:06:48,549
Shut up

535
01:06:48,720 --> 01:06:51,518
If I was afraid of you,
I wouldn't have been with you

536
01:07:05,280 --> 01:07:08,158
Extra…Come for the Extra…

537
01:07:09,120 --> 01:07:11,475
Give me one

538
01:07:12,560 --> 01:07:13,913
"Son of Yu Zhen Ting is kidnapped"

539
01:07:54,840 --> 01:07:56,432
Any news?

540
01:07:56,600 --> 01:07:57,715
Yes

541
01:07:58,880 --> 01:08:00,518
How much they want?

542
01:08:00,640 --> 01:08:02,790
Nothing

543
01:08:02,960 --> 01:08:05,315
Want me to leave Shanghai

544
01:08:07,240 --> 01:08:10,277
I should have left earlier

545
01:08:11,280 --> 01:08:16,195
There won't be a happy ending
for a person like me

546
01:08:22,440 --> 01:08:23,395
I have already handed over

547
01:08:23,560 --> 01:08:26,597
half of the business here to you

548
01:08:26,760 --> 01:08:29,911
Send someone to handle the other half

549
01:08:31,960 --> 01:08:32,790
I'll leave tomorrow

550
01:08:32,960 --> 01:08:35,110
Brother, don't be upset

551
01:08:35,240 --> 01:08:38,357
We'll think of something
when Xiao Kai comes back

552
01:08:39,520 --> 01:08:41,192
Never mind

553
01:08:41,920 --> 01:08:44,718
Gen Bao, you've been with me

554
01:08:44,880 --> 01:08:46,791
ever since the Knife gang first started

555
01:08:46,920 --> 01:08:48,672
He's my only son

556
01:08:48,840 --> 01:08:51,354
Don't be too harsh on him

557
01:08:51,520 --> 01:08:53,750
Boss, what do you mean?

558
01:08:54,920 --> 01:08:56,831
Gen Bao, never mind

559
01:08:56,960 --> 01:09:01,078
Qiu Lian Huan wouldn't put up
such conditions

560
01:09:01,200 --> 01:09:02,235
At the club

561
01:09:02,400 --> 01:09:05,472
he left after he received a call
from friends

562
01:09:05,600 --> 01:09:08,956
Although I am old, I am not stupid

563
01:09:09,080 --> 01:09:10,035
If you suspect me

564
01:09:10,200 --> 01:09:12,191
I'll go with you

565
01:09:13,560 --> 01:09:15,152
No need

566
01:09:15,680 --> 01:09:18,990
Gen Bao, be careful

567
01:09:19,120 --> 01:09:22,795
You'll be treated the same way
you treat others

568
01:09:51,160 --> 01:09:52,991
When I leave tomorrow

569
01:09:53,120 --> 01:09:55,111
will you go with me?

570
01:09:55,280 --> 01:09:56,679
We'll stay with Master Zeng

571
01:09:56,840 --> 01:10:00,799
Alright

572
01:10:02,480 --> 01:10:05,233
Master Zeng has an errand for us

573
01:10:05,360 --> 01:10:07,590
Master Yu, please don't blame us

574
01:10:08,680 --> 01:10:10,398
Ask Gen Bao to come to me

575
01:10:10,920 --> 01:10:14,993
Master Zeng went to examine goods
at some companies

576
01:10:18,040 --> 01:10:20,235
You…

577
01:11:32,520 --> 01:11:33,873
Xiao Kai has been caught

578
01:11:34,040 --> 01:11:36,998
The one who caught Xiao Kai
claimed to be your man

579
01:11:38,880 --> 01:11:40,438
I've been to the club

580
01:11:40,600 --> 01:11:42,795
and they said that Yu Zhen Ting is dead

581
01:11:42,960 --> 01:11:44,632
Zeng Gen Bao is taking care of his funeral

582
01:11:44,760 --> 01:11:46,432
They also said that Zeng Gen Bao

583
01:11:46,600 --> 01:11:48,352
has taken over
all of Yu Zhen Ting's business

584
01:11:48,520 --> 01:11:51,114
I'm afraid
Xiao Kai might have been killed too

585
01:11:52,200 --> 01:11:53,872
The matter is now very clear

586
01:11:54,040 --> 01:11:56,634
It's Zeng Gen Bao
who is playing all the tricks

587
01:11:56,800 --> 01:12:00,588
He is now more powerful
than Yu Zhen Ting used to be

588
01:12:15,240 --> 01:12:19,870
No matter how powerful he is,
I've to find him

589
01:12:22,600 --> 01:12:24,636
Better wait until you recuperate

590
01:12:29,360 --> 01:12:33,751
Ju Fang, I made you so happy last night

591
01:12:33,920 --> 01:12:36,434
how can you say that I haven't recuperated

592
01:12:53,480 --> 01:12:55,596
Tonight I must go and find some help

593
01:12:55,760 --> 01:12:58,752
otherwise he'll grow in power

594
01:12:58,920 --> 01:13:00,672
and make it more difficult
to deal with him

595
01:14:02,920 --> 01:14:06,549
You've got into big troubles

596
01:14:07,280 --> 01:14:09,714
you'd better go on hiding

597
01:14:09,880 --> 01:14:14,078
If you are in need of money,
I can give it to you

598
01:14:14,240 --> 01:14:15,912
What I've mentioned just now…

599
01:14:19,160 --> 01:14:21,037
It's not much, please don't mind

600
01:14:21,480 --> 01:14:22,879
This is…

601
01:14:31,520 --> 01:14:34,592
Zeng Gen Bao is looking for you

602
01:14:34,760 --> 01:14:36,955
You can't stay here for long

603
01:14:54,880 --> 01:14:55,790
What's wrong?

604
01:14:55,960 --> 01:14:58,679
Your boss and I are sworn brothers

605
01:15:04,920 --> 01:15:05,989
"Sworn brothers"

606
01:15:11,720 --> 01:15:14,359
Don't worry, your troubles are mine too

607
01:15:14,520 --> 01:15:18,354
Make yourself at home

608
01:15:19,960 --> 01:15:22,599
Those who I called friends all deserted me

609
01:15:23,400 --> 01:15:24,628
It isn't like that

610
01:15:35,720 --> 01:15:38,917
I still need to go somewhere else,
we'll be in touch

611
01:15:41,480 --> 01:15:42,549
Don't go

612
01:15:43,360 --> 01:15:44,759
Why?

613
01:15:44,920 --> 01:15:49,755
Brother, since you are here
we should have a chat

614
01:15:52,720 --> 01:15:57,635
Alright, this is what good friends are for

615
01:16:22,040 --> 01:16:25,396
When Zeng Gen Bao comes,
give him my regards

616
01:17:14,760 --> 01:17:15,954
Geng Sheng

617
01:17:16,120 --> 01:17:20,511
None of those who are with us
are human enough

618
01:17:21,600 --> 01:17:25,229
Neither of us are

619
01:17:50,920 --> 01:17:53,388
"Qing Lin Tower"

620
01:17:54,240 --> 01:17:58,153
Newspapers…Come for a newspaper

621
01:18:00,040 --> 01:18:02,270
Newspapers…

622
01:18:50,600 --> 01:18:53,831
Master Qiu, you have guts

623
01:18:54,920 --> 01:18:56,512
You too

624
01:18:56,680 --> 01:18:58,511
Yu Zhen Ting has helped you before

625
01:18:58,640 --> 01:19:00,073
how can you treat him like this?

626
01:19:00,200 --> 01:19:02,998
It's a world where the fittest survive

627
01:19:03,160 --> 01:19:04,718
You are right

628
01:19:25,920 --> 01:19:30,277
Qiu Lian Huan,
beg for pardon and you'll be alright

629
01:19:30,400 --> 01:19:31,879
I definitely won't

630
01:19:32,040 --> 01:19:35,476
I am tired of this life

631
01:21:11,400 --> 01:21:13,311
Sorry, please leave now

632
01:21:13,480 --> 01:21:15,038
Go…

633
01:22:00,680 --> 01:22:01,874
Grab the weapons

634
01:22:22,280 --> 01:22:24,953
Master Zeng looks highly on me after all

635
01:22:25,120 --> 01:22:27,588
You've even sent your favourite Knife gang

636
01:22:27,760 --> 01:22:31,150
Qiu Lian Huan, you have two options

637
01:22:31,280 --> 01:22:33,475
One is to serve me

638
01:22:33,640 --> 01:22:34,993
If you do

639
01:22:35,120 --> 01:22:37,395
you'll be my right hand

640
01:22:37,560 --> 01:22:42,475
If not, you'll die

641
01:22:43,800 --> 01:22:46,268
I'd rather die than to serve you

642
01:22:46,320 --> 01:22:50,108
But even if I have to die

643
01:22:50,360 --> 01:22:52,828
I'll avenge for Lin Geng Sheng first

644
01:24:21,520 --> 01:24:23,238
"Hui Le Lane"

645
01:27:03,720 --> 01:27:05,278
Qiu Lian Huan has just been stabbed

646
01:27:05,440 --> 01:27:08,193
His stomach is cut open,
don't be afraid of him

647
01:27:30,840 --> 01:27:32,273
Kill him

648
01:27:33,080 --> 01:27:34,957
Qiu Lian Huan is finished

649
01:30:25,480 --> 01:30:26,833
Attack

650
01:32:50,320 --> 01:32:51,912
Go…hurry

651
01:33:31,840 --> 01:33:34,149
"Qiu Lian Huan was killed"

